headline: Bio-Techne (TECH) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of life sciences company Bio-Techne (NASDAQ:TECH) jumped 4.6% in the afternoon session after the investment firm Stephens initiated coverage on the stock with an "overweight" rating and a $65.00 price target.
